Class BigIntMatrix

  • java.lang.Object
    • finnmath.linear.Matrix<java.math.BigInteger,BigIntVector,BigIntMatrix>
      • finnmath.linear.BigIntMatrix

  • @Beta
public final class BigIntMatrix
extends Matrix<java.math.BigInteger,BigIntVector,BigIntMatrix>
    An immutable implementation of a matrix which is based on ImmutableTable and uses BigInteger as type for its entries

    1
